data.description: Bluestone ~ Private and enchanting estate, unlike any other in Washoe Valley.  Situated on a private water-ski lake in Hidden Lake Ranch this custom European-style home features superior quality finishes throughout, including a one-of-a-kind hand sculpted white Carrara marble Roman statue mantel imported from Europe, marble columns, chef's kitchen and butler's kitchen, carved boulder soaking tub imported from Bali; private guest quarters, a private beach, workshop, and expansive outdoor entertainment patio. Some of the finishes throughout include granite tile, Carrara marble, natural stone, Aldwerwood moldings and doors, beautiful lighting fixtures, and exquisite bathroom materials.  Additionally, a new pump house with a second water filtration system (separate from the interior) has been installed to accommodate the outside landscaping.  Adding to the appeal of this exceptional offering is its private lake setting, yet convenient location to Reno and world-renowned Lake Tahoe, plus the perk of Nevada's tax-friendly environment.
